Handle multiple `-J ITEM`?

```suggestion
    in_minus_J = False
    ret = []
    for flag in flags:
        if in_minus_J:
            in_minus_J = False
            continue
        if flag == '-J':
             in_minus_J = True
        else:
             ret.append(flag)
```

